data.description: Escape City Life on 1.2 Acres complete with solar energy system offering savings against rising energy cost. Beautifully maintained 2020 home with Open floor plan, Spacious Kitchen, 5 Bedrooms, 3 Full Baths, and large utility room. Above ground pool and deck to beat this summer heat. Storage building with electricity plus an additional building that has endless possibilities could be used as office space or guest studio with electricity already ran and ready to be hooked up. Bring your Family, Friends, and animals to enjoy country living with an easy commute to work with approximately 25 miles to Dallas. All information to be verified by buyer and buyers agent. Room dimensions are approximate buyer to verify room sizes and square footage.
